The Deputy Governor of Adamawa State, Crowther Seth, has lost his mother. Mama Helina Metosudo died on Tuesday at the age of 118, according to information obtained Tuesday evening. The deputy governor who confirmed the incident to newsmen, said Mama died in the early hours of Tuesday. He said her remains would be interred at her birthplace, Lamurde, in Lamurde Local Government Area on Saturday, October 17.